lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + space_expansion_backfires&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The sweet-spot view: the capability that settles planets also moves asteroids and exports nationalism off-world (Deudney, Dark Skies), and genuinely decorrelated self-sufficient settlements are far further away than boosterism assumes (Weinersmiths, A City on Mars) — so below a large number of independent settlements, expansion ADDS anthropogenic risk, and accelerating it before geopolitics matures is net-negative. The perils window stays open far longer, the expected future shrinks, and x-risk work keeps its urgency but loses most of its astronomical multiplier. Mutually exclusive with the time-of-perils-exit reading. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 15 space_expansion_backfires" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbOztmy5Hc7lwPSxtktNukWSYpiURcuLdEWL5KoI6ko3m72t%2B%2BQlGw5sRED%2FtIq8vCZZ145ox8nAV2QLFLveUBPxietFpyfn8O9ICwBxcEX5I8VPuQJTLO263Uh5yIKHhnNIfdmvVl%2F5vWgJhVPwevV9eFpgiAXUmZxqhhPwA8RawwupERwP2Qk0lDeqA0eLIiYkZysZmEWk0SWP%2FRgkalM0OL1LCZKUTHLmQpnAZM%2BzxLFkmUp3oeEV9%2FPtk6vtfVApsSnM%2FqU4mukNpsT%2F2HBBJWG84T4IZANcSaBwKeVCvF5wSIK6JLNz7IFKiQKSBDIBgiKfmQJlcCFARO0ifaSmCJxJvG9Cql1xb8kWpf4BuMMfB6nXGpj1gJ4NgkoIuIrZqlJRZKARDyhEGOgIge%2Br%2BMwefyuqerjaBn1FR58JFFGgS8MwiZkjgF7R6WCebaCTKvRByWtGjaGiw8gyYKqFdRuaZBzHsAtChHhh3WL8fPk4%2BT24n5yCfMVLGlCBVHUSVdlltCAqS1nneKPDYyTspS0PxHJYH1OfCqUNjzmArNj7TdpZa1TSJpGjEoH7laxE%2FFlwkVMotqPtNeAdNR7rhssE7OR%2BxO8%2F3BmJOdUEfs2FXxO5ixiConMuTY%2B0Cn%2B1W2A982BK%2BIrjjqJoBYKBVIdiUQ1QHKgOj24WGL8Jl%2Fzy4vr31v%2F%2BAZzGvEc81ifNXGmT%2FgcrfA4YqNvDRbqDjJf2YhgDCkmIJpv8%2FSyyFw4x4oALY0vm4rFFP4NPlFEKsFTPKarIMmISU6dk0Q0LUIR79otiSVdte7Qdwn85f7UWgl4lPCRiyAkmYS%2FPKenX56honMMBpRFg84ztfGuKIgb7AhM%2B1ug3CuHYzE7btu4XT%2F2n%2BuGthIs1ry2MrEgmIe6gDCD0DPr%2BtNFQkRsczckfxARQO