><object label="Living in&lt;br&gt;a simulation&lt;br&gt;[1+5+6+15+16]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   5k lives-eq/$1k · 50% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up ALLFED · 37%&lt;br&gt;(Nick Bostrom)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + space_expansion_backfires + living_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WPtv2zgS%2FlcGwe2dnfND8tvO5YA8nN3ikm6RpCgWdeHSEm3xIok6koqj7Wb%2F9huSki3HNmLA2F9aR6K%2B%2BeY9wx8nPp2TNFRX3Kcno5NmE87Pz%2BFREBaD4uAJ8nuGP5YxTNKW43ZgyUXoPzO6hKU77U57U7c7dXtQkYon4Paq%2BvtJjDgXUqZRohiPwQsQbgQOJERwL2Ak1GjusAUuzImYkiXJpkEakVgWL7owT1UqaP54GhGlqJgumQqmPpMeT2PF4kVxvAcxLz%2Bfbny9ktYFmRCPTulLgo%2BR2nRGvKc5E3R9pgche9YQLJ5KFqUh0ToYlcbEC4Cs9WISCHzKVIC%2F5yykgEZbv5ZNUAFRQHxf1kBQtDSLURAXBkzQOpqDRBT1YhKfq4BaS%2F1DovKxZzDOwONRwqXWdXUAv419ioj4iEmDJhWJfRLymEKErgwb8H3lqfHzd01Vf46KU0%2Fhh88kTCnwuUFYO7VhwC6pVDBLM0i1GP2hpGXFRnDxASSZU5VB5Z76S859uMdDRHhB1WL8PP44vr94HF%2FDLIMFjakgijaSrIgj6jO1YaxTfFlDNypLSdsTkQzW59ijQmnFIy4weFZ2k%2FasNQpJkpBR2YCHLGqEfBFzEZGw8iPp1iAZdl%2BrBsv4bOj8BFcfzszJGVXEPk0En5EZC5lCIjOulfd1Enx1auB%2Ba8AN8RRHmURQC4UHEu2JWNVAcqA6PLhYoP%2FGX5fXF7e%2FNf%2F2DWY05EsMc%2F2t8TN9wd9hhp8jNtrWYKFsP%2FWU9Qj6kGJ8ovo2jK%2FzwIZzTBjQp%2FFhXbGIwj%2FBI4pIJXiCn%2BkkiVMTsKBjkoi6Rcj9XbknkaRZ8wFtF8Ofzk%2FNTMCzhI9c%2BAFJJfzpNrr64RkKOkdnQJFTaDyTOpd5vtxhzWDa3gLPbRkcc73htIzZ9c%2Fea9XQVoJFmtdGJOYEl4F